msg: java2wsdl was not picking up the package properly to construct schema/wsdl targetnamespace when used from the java2wsdl ant task (AntClassLoader has problems with getPackage()). So pickup the pkg from the className itself. Another problem clazz.getName() strips out the pkg prefix, so pass in className.
